race.comment: Tricky race. MR MAGNUS (4) was an impressive winner first up at Caulfield Heath, coming from last over this distance to get up by a long neck. Stays at 1000m here and draws wide but the big track will suit and he can finish over the top again. SOPHAST (11) got through the very heavy conditions here to score well last time out. Different scenario now but draws the pole and can measure up again. LUNAR MODULE (5) is off a let-up for a new yard. Her best 1000m form reads very well for this if she can recapture it. GO TO HOLLYWOOD (12) hasn't won in a while but was good to the line last start and sets up very similarly.
